Hello! Welcome to my Turo hosting pageI My name is Elliott. My cohost Samantha and I are here to serve the Palm Springs area with competitively priced, well maintained and carefully curated vehicles for your business and leisure needs. We have been helping the palm springs area for 3+ years. All of Our vehicles are given to our guests vacuumed thoroughly of the cabin and upholstery, hand detailed exterior and disinfected interior, all for our guests enjoyment. 


Larger bodied. Powerful ride. Best sound system.


“Large Marge” is our 2011 Ford Escape. V6 engine. Seats 5 comfortably. Trunk is very large great for luggage and golf bags. Tan interior with golden exterior. Fantastic sound system.

“Betty Wyatt” is our 2014 Ford F-150. White exterior with gray interior. V8 engine. Seats three. XL bed great for hauling. Great sound system. Lined floors for easy clean up.

“Jambi” is our 2014 Kia Sedona. Dolphin blue exterior gray leather interior. Seats seven ( heated front seats), four doors (automatic passenger rear and trunk). Sun/moon roof, back up camera in rear view mirror and satellite radio.


Our medium cabin. Spacious trunk. Highway advantage. Drive your friends comfortably. 

“Jude” is our 2013 Nissan Sentra. Four doors with microfiber light grey interior. Eco/sport mode.

“MJ” is our second 2013 Nissan Sentra. Pearl white exterior with microfiber charcoal interior. Standard radio.  Eco/sport mode.


Economically efficient. Smaller cabin. Great gas mileage. Good sound. Petite rear seating.


“Antoinette” is our 2014 Ford Fiesta. Red exterior. Four door hatch back. Black fabric interior. LED ambient lighting. Bluetooth capable.

“Toby” is our 2016 Ford Fiesta. Four door, hatchback with LED lighting in the interior. Black exterior and interior. Bluetooth capable.

“Lucille” is our 2014 Nissan Versa. Tinted back windows and black interior. kenwood radio and bluetooth.

“Blueberry” is our 2014 Nissan Versa. Tinted back windows and gray interior. Has J.V.C radio with Bluetooth capability.

Thank you for shopping our vehicles! We want YOU in OUR selected rides for enhanced freedom for you and your passengers as you traverse the Palm Springs and greater areas! 

All of our vehicles are 100% insured. We always recommend adding insurance to your Turo package.

Smoking in any of our vehicles is against Turo terms of use. If smoking is found in the forms of ashes, burns, odor it will be reported to Turo trust and safety department as part of quality control. Turo May charge $150 for violating the no smoking terms of 

Vehicle delivery may be optional for an additional fee of $120 depending on team availability (delivery fee sliding scale, personal message for best value ). You designate where vehicle is dropped off and picked up. We are now capable of ZERO contact delivery. If you desire zero contact delivery you will be asked to verify identity and license by photo.

On time pick up is 30 minutes before or after your selected trip start time. Avoid loss of trip by communicating any time issues or you may lose your trip. Flight delays are exempt.

Reimbursement must be requested immediately after trip end to be applicable.

Updated 4/6/2022

bio.openEndedText:
My wife Jhana and I started Turo in 2023 with the intent to help people be able to rent cars much more efficiently than at Car Rental companies.  We have traveled quite a bit over the last 5+ years and realized Car Rental Companies at times can be a pain in the you know what!  :(  Also, the customer experience is not always the best.  We wanted to change that experience.  Plus, we absolutely love cars and are car enthusiasts.  We appreciate you as our guests and hope that your experience is flawless with us.  My wife is a stay-at-home mom, grandma and dog mom.  I am a Director of Sales for a School Bus and Commercial & Transit Bus Dealership in Southern California.  We hope to Host you soon!  Take Care and drive safe!

PS: We currently have a 2012 Blue Fiat 500 Lounge, 2012 Black Toyota Camry, 2013 Red Fiat 500 Pop, 2013 Green Fiat 500 Pop, White 2014 Toyota Corolla, White 2017 Subaru Forester Touring AWD, White 2019 Range Rover Velar S-Dynamic, a Light Gray/Silver 2021 Dodge Challenger SXT, a White 2021 Chevy Silverado Crew Cab Long Bed, 2022 Blue Toyota Corolla SE and should have 3-5 additional vehicles on our platform by the end of summer 2024.  We are also looking to co-host your vehicle.  Reach out if interested.  

Ride On...........    :)

Sincerely,
Jason & Jhana
The Cargivers
CEO @ NVIS AI, Navy Vet
